sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Page as TaskKanbanPage
    participant API as api/client.js
    participant Server as Express
    participant DB as SQLite

    Note over User,DB: === 1. 加载项目看板 ===

    User->>Page: 选择项目
    Page->>Page: setProjectId(id)
    Page->>API: GET /api/tasks?project_id=X
    API->>Server: HTTP GET
    Server->>DB: SELECT * FROM tasks WHERE project_id=X AND deleted_at IS NULL ORDER BY sort_order
    DB-->>Server: Task[]
    Server-->>API: {ok, data: Task[]}
    API-->>Page: Task[]

    par 并行加载
        Page->>API: GET /api/projects/X
        API->>Server: HTTP GET
        Server->>DB: SELECT * FROM projects WHERE id=X
        DB-->>Server: Project
        Server-->>API: {ok, data: Project}
        API-->>Page: Project
    and
        Page->>API: GET /api/projects/X/kanban-stats
        API->>Server: HTTP GET
        Server->>DB: SELECT COUNT...
        DB-->>Server: stats
        Server-->>API: {ok, data: KanbanStats}
        API-->>Page: KanbanStats
    end

    Page->>Page: 拆分为 todoTasks / doneTasks
    Page->>Page: localStorage 读取折叠状态
    Page->>Page: 渲染 KanbanProjectView

    Note over User,DB: === 2. 展开子任务 ===

    User->>Page: 点击 ▶ 箭头
    Page->>Page: setExpanded(true)
    Page->>API: GET /api/tasks/{taskId}/subtasks
    API->>Server: HTTP GET
    Server->>DB: SELECT * FROM subtasks WHERE task_id=? AND deleted_at IS NULL ORDER BY sort_order
    DB-->>Server: Subtask[]
    Server-->>API: {ok, data: Subtask[]}
    API-->>Page: Subtask[]
    Page->>Page: 渲染 SubtaskList，自动聚焦输入框

    Note over User,DB: === 3. 新增子任务（快速录入 + 乐观更新） ===

    User->>Page: 输入文字 + 回车
    Page->>Page: 乐观插入本地状态
    Page->>Page: 清空输入框，保持光标
    Page->>API: POST /api/tasks/{taskId}/subtasks {title}
    API->>Server: HTTP POST
    Server->>DB: INSERT INTO subtasks (task_id, title, sort_order) VALUES (?, ?, ?)
    DB-->>Server: {id, ...}
    Server-->>API: {ok, data: Subtask}
    API-->>Page: Subtask（含真实 id）
    Page->>Page: 用服务端数据更新本地记录

    Note over User,DB: === 4. 拖拽排序（乐观更新 + 滚动保持） ===

    User->>Page: 拖拽任务卡片到新位置
    Page->>Page: onDragEnd → 计算新 sort_order
    Page->>Page: 记录 scrollTop
    Page->>Page: 乐观重排本地 tasks[] 数组
    Page->>API: PUT /api/tasks/{taskId}/reorder {sort_order, project_id}
    API->>Server: HTTP PUT
    Server->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION; 重新计算 sort_order; COMMIT
    DB-->>Server: OK
    Server-->>API: {ok, data: Task}
    API-->>Page: OK
    Page->>Page: requestAnimationFrame 恢复 scrollTop

    Note over User,DB: === 5. 切换完成状态（乐观更新 + 自动折叠） ===

    User->>Page: 点击 ✓ 按钮
    Page->>Page: 乐观移动：todo→done
    Page->>API: PUT /api/tasks/{id}/toggle-complete
    API->>Server: HTTP PUT
    Server->>DB: UPDATE tasks SET completed_at=?, kanban_column=?, status=? WHERE id=?
    DB-->>Server: OK
    Server-->>API: {ok, data: Task}
    API-->>Page: Task（含 completed_at）
    Page->>Page: 检查全部完成 → 自动折叠
    Page->>Page: localStorage.setItem('kanban-collapsed-{pid}', 'true')
